chart.name: Index Statistics
chart.programText:
A = data('gauge.indices.total.store.size', filter=filter('plugin', 'elasticsearch') and filter('plugin_instance', 'elasticsearch'), extrapolation='last_value').mean(by=['index']).publish(label='A')

chart.description: p99 latency over the last hour
chart.name: Top Indexes by Query Latency (ms)
chart.programText:
A = data('counter.indices.total.search.query-total', filter=filter('plugin', 'elasticsearch'), rollup='max').max(by=['index']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('counter.indices.total.search.query-time', filter=filter('plugin', 'elasticsearch'), rollup='max').max(by=['index']).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A).timeshift('1h').publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (B).timeshift('1h').publish(label='D', enable=False)
E = ((B-D)/(A-C)).publish(label='E', enable=False)
F = (E).percentile(pct=99, by=['index']).top(count=5).publish(label='F')
